Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.15,0:00:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much to everyone\N who is going to watch this movie now.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.86,0:00:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is me from sixty years ago, \Na really cute Kayo-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.25,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She puts the current me to shame.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This movie...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.07,0:00:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Its main point is to depict parental love,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.07,0:00:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will also tell you about the cruelty \Nand wastefulness of war.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.46,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope there will never be a war again.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.03,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last war, I lost my parents, my siblings, and my grandmother: six people in all.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a war orphan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.15,0:00:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But even as an orphan, I lived on with all I had.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.36,0:00:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was the love of my parents \Nand my siblings that allowed me to do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.23,0:00:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In tough times, sad times, and painful times, \NI always remembered my parents.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.56,0:01:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're a cheerful, resilient, \Nand strong girl, so you'll be fine."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These reassuring words of my mother \Nwould come back to me. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.25,0:01:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I also remember my youngest brother calling out to me "Sis, sis!" {15:03 of the main feature}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.36,0:01:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the bad things in life \Ndidn't seem so bad anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.68,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Let's live a bright, lively, and energetic life, smiling."\NThose words from my mother always reassured me.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think a parent's love is a precious thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.94,0:01:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And if watching this film makes you think, \N"It's incredible how strong children can be,"
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.49,0:01:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that'd make me so, so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.88,0:01:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,War is an infinitely foolish, cruel, and wasteful enterprise. That's what I wanted to convey.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.45,0:01:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch it, everyone.
